    "body" : "<p>You can convert Date to LocalDate. Its has plus methods, like plusYears(),plusMonths(),plusDays().</p>\n<pre><code>    // Date -&gt; LocalDate\n    private static LocalDate of(Date date) {\n        Instant instant = date.toInstant();\n        return instant.atZone(ZoneId.systemDefault()).toLocalDate();\n    }\n \n    // LocalDate -&gt; Date\n    private static Date of(LocalDate localDate) {\n        Instant instant = localDate.atStartOfDay(ZoneId.systemDefault()).toInstant();\n        return Date.from(instant);\n    }\n</code></pre>\n"
